{
  "type": "html-list",
  "title": "목록 HTML 템플릿",
  "html_template": "<div class=\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4\">\n    <h2>게시판</h2>\n    <!--@if(userId)-->\n    <a href=\"write.jsp\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">글쓰기</a>\n    <!--/if(userId)-->\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card shadow-sm mb-4\">\n    <div class=\"card-body\">\n        <form name=\"form1\" method=\"get\" class=\"row g-3\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-10\">\n                <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" name=\"keyword\" placeholder=\"제목 또는 내용으로 검색\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-2\">\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary w-100\">검색</button>\n            </div>\n        </form>\n    </div>\n</div>\n{{form_script}}\n\n<div class=\"card shadow-sm\">\n    <div class=\"card-body\">\n        <p class=\"text-muted mb-3\">전체 <strong>{{total}}</strong>개의 게시글</p>\n\n        <div class=\"table-responsive\">\n            <table class=\"table table-hover\">\n                <thead class=\"table-light\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <th width=\"80\" class=\"text-center\">번호</th>\n                        <th>제목</th>\n                        <th width=\"120\" class=\"text-center\">작성자</th>\n                        <th width=\"100\" class=\"text-center\">조회수</th>\n                        <th width=\"150\" class=\"text-center\">작성일</th>\n                    </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody>\n                    <!--@loop(list)-->\n                    <tr>\n                        <td class=\"text-center\">{{list.id}}</td>\n                        <td>\n                            <a href=\"view.jsp?id={{list.id}}\" class=\"text-decoration-none\">\n                                {{list.title}}\n                            </a>\n                        </td>\n                        <td class=\"text-center\">{{list.user_name}}</td>\n                        <td class=\"text-center\">{{list.hit}}</td>\n                        <td class=\"text-center\">{{list.reg_date_format}}</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <!--/loop(list)-->\n                </tbody>\n            </table>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"text-center mt-4\">\n            {{pager}}\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
  "notes": [
    "Bootstrap 5 카드 레이아웃 사용",
    "{{total}}: ListManager에서 p.setVar()로 전달한 총 건수",
    "{{pager}}: ListManager.getPaging()이 생성한 페이징 HTML",
    "{{form_script}}: f.getScript()가 생성한 클라이언트 검증 JS",
    "@loop(list): DataSet 반복 출력",
    "@if(userId): 로그인 시에만 글쓰기 버튼 표시",
    "{{list.reg_date_format}}: JSP에서 info.put()으로 가공한 날짜"
  ]
}
